degrees hot. And this happens to millions of tons of material everywhere. This rapidly heats up the

05:47.200 --> 05:53.120
atmosphere to insane temperatures. We don't know exactly how hot it got or how long this heat shock

05:53.120 --> 05:58.640
lasted. But there are two ideas here. Either the air was heated to hundreds of degrees for a few

05:58.640 --> 06:04.720
minutes, or 2000s of degrees for around one minute. In any case, the air became as hot as the

