07:33.440 --> 07:39.440
marine reptiles and ammonites that used to dominate the seas. The biosphere that survivors

07:39.440 --> 07:46.240
now find themselves in is like an alien landscape. Ash, debris, and the burned remains of the formerly

07:46.240 --> 07:53.600
lush and blooming life cover the ground. The sky is dark and it's cold and fresh food is scarce,

